name: Time Travel Skeleton exe
description:
Time Travel Skeleton.exe

After Dying a while, the Skeleton remembers that  he got a Very Important thing to do .

So He wake up as a Skeleton head and Finish the thing that he forgot to do before dying.

The Player need to use the time travel ability to get through the level。

-5 minute game content.

-Prototype

-Made in 3 day with unity.

-No Option

- Low resolution.

-First  Game Jam. (Mini Game Jam 43: Travel)
